				h1.articleheading WHO IS DEADEYE?
				p.articletext Raised in a warzone, the mercenary known as Deadeye lived day and night with a gun in her hand. As she escaped this world alongside her estranged sister, she kept the gun on her waist. And now, the gun has made her rich, powerful and feared. 

				p.articletext These days, Deadeye is on a permanent contract with Knox's Villain Underground. During this time, DEADEYE has quickly gained a reputation as one of the world's deadliest marksmen. Despite her constant disgust with the team's antics, Deadeye has proved to be a dangerous and loyal ally to the Villain Underground. Underestimate her at your own risk - it takes a cold-blooded killer to stand tall in a world filled with superhumans. 
